title: War of the Roses: One Trap After Another
description: Kylie is finding red flag after red flag with her boyfriend Tony.  It started with lipstick on a mug, then an earring in the couch, and then she set up a trap to see if he was cheating when he went out of town but that didn't work.  So now she's doing War of the Roses to try to catch him once and for all.
